    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      AUTO_ADJUSTED
      after the bounds got auto-adjusted, this status will set.
      FIX
      means that the bounds are fix (manually) and are not to be auto-adjusted.
      INITIAL
      initial means that the bounds gets auto adjusted if they are not manual.
      READJUST_AFTER_SCALE
      this flags the status that a scale was done and the bounds has to be auto-adjusted afterwards.
